SS- is the expected amount left over between orders. Extra inventory on hold in case lead time is larger than expected. You need to be able to fulfill RQ poicy to make sure the demand is fulfilled.
variables needed to consider are the Demand- or need for product. How many customers that want the product, and the frequency of time the product is being sold. You dont want to have to much or else you will incur cost, and you dont want to have less because then you will lose potential revenue
